{"title":"「长乐国庆集训2018ROUND1」5. 树","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5160#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=5160","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5160/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/5160/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/5160"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"给定一棵 $n$ 个节点，以 $S$ 为根的树，边有权，删掉一条边的代价为这条边的边权。\r\n\n\r\n\n现在你要删除若干条边，使得根节点 $S$ 不能到达任何叶子节点。请求出最小的代价和。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入第一行两个整数 $n，S$ 表示树的节点个数和根。\r\n\n\r\n\n接下来 $n-1$ 行每行三个整数 $a、b、c$，表示 $a、b$ 之间有一条代价为 $c$ 的边。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出包含一行，一个整数，表示最小代价。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入样例1：\r\n\r\n```\r\n4 1\r\n1 2 1\r\n1 3 1\r\n1 4 1\r\n```\r\n\r\n输出样例1：\r\n\r\n```\r\n3\r\n```\r\n\r\n输入样例2：\r\n\r\n```\r\n4 1\r\n1 2 3\r\n2 3 1\r\n3 4 2\r\n```\r\n\r\n输出样例2：\r\n\r\n```\r\n1\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 $20\\%$ 的数据，$n\\le 10$。\r\n\n\r\n\n对于 $50\\%$ 的数据，$n\\le 1000$。\r\n\n\r\n\n对于 $100\\%$ 的数据，$n\\le 100000$。"}]}